  "key_strengths": [
    "Coverage of four major reporting guidelines (CONSORT, STROBE, PRISMA, TRIPOD) provides broad applicability",
    "Mandatory clarification of study design before guideline selection prevents wrong-guideline application",
    "Mandatory/recommended/optional item classification for each guideline provides actionable prioritization",
    "Reviewer-risk classification for missing items focuses user attention on highest-impact gaps"
